column2: I want cocaine so bad I can almost taste it.
I have an urge for cocaine.
I am going to use cocaine as soon as possible.
I think that I could resist using "coke" now.
All I want to use now is cocaine.
I have no desire for cocaine right now.
Using cocaine now would make things seem just perfect.
I will use cocaine as soon as I get the chance.
Nothing would be better than using "coke" right now.
